page.title: 13INTER VILLAGE COMPETITION
page.content: Each year WEST NORFOLK DISTRICT COUNCIL organise a village competition on one Sunday in June.The sports included in the competition are: netball,football,table tennis, darts and obstacle races.One competition is for under 16's and one for over 16's.The various teams practice separately with a few of them continuing as a club for most of the year.At this years competition the Walpole St. Peter team finished 4th and the Walpole St. Andrew team 7th. With the new parish boundaries they will form just one team in the future.
